Since the data is random dataset,we just split the data directly

#divide data into training dataset and testing dataset
Training <- Retention[1:(170*0.8),]
Testing <- Retention[137:170,]

Then we create our first model where tstsc is predictor and apret is responsed variable.

model1 <- lm(apret~tstsc,data = Training)
